You know... I don't know what to believe anymore... I have had so many people stab me in the back or lie to me.. tell something to my face and say the opposite to someone else.. how can one self be so mean? but that's life... I hate it when someone says "I have never lied to you" but you find out from one of your birdy friends that he/she did.. or he/she is lying.. 

Now that I think of it.. I can understand why "someone" can't keep a girlfriend... HE never has his head on straight. I once thought he was the one for me.. but now I'm startin not to.. I hate puttin up with someone who is really childish bout certain topics. It's fun to play games... but not screw u over games. I'm sick of being screwed over... and pushed aside.. Maybe It will stop one day. but you know. you can't control your fuckin heart... I've tried. don't work. Wish I could be like - STOP LIKIN HIM! but it don't work like that either

*sigh* Maybe I'm wrong bout all this... I don't know.. sorta hope I am... because I don't wanna loose him. I've grown so close to him. He's one of my best friends and I don't wanna loose what we have and you know.. I don't wanna give up either.. you learn from ur mistakes And I hope he comes to realize.. if you don't act fast you will loose a really good friend who doesn't care bout your past and never gives up on you! Man...Already lost one best friend over somethin stupid.. don't wanna loose another.

<FONT color=#ffff66>OH MY F-ING GOD! Warped Tour Kicked Major Ass! It was so much fun. 

Got to verizon bout 10ish -10:30ish. Text Josh and Ash, they found us and we waited in line then finally got in. EVERY Time you turned around, you were given free shit. every tent you went to - free cds/buttons/stickers. I GOT A LOT OF FREE STUFF! 

Durin My Chemical Romance ( were the best( I love them ) ) A weak moshpit was started (well it was big to me because I'm so small hehe) well pushing and shoving and bodies flyin over ya was a lot of sweaty fun until Brandon fell and his lense popped out - couldn't find it! so we had to leave MCR's perfomance to call his mom and him go out to the car and get his contacts. that sucked. but We DID meet  a lot of bands that are just now starting out and heard a wittle bit of most of them too. Several of them weren't that bad. 

- all day long walking and looking. 6 stages!  And the last band that played was Hawthorne Heights.   VERY GOOD.   

We got Senses Fail and Thrice's autograph. I wanted Matchbook Romance and Hawthorne Heights but we didn't find out about it in time. I also wanted My Chemical Romance and FallOutBoy but they weren't signing. :(  Josh, Ash, Brandon, nor me got to see FallOutBoy. because we were in line for Thrice's autograph. We heard them though - they sounded gre-e-e-a-a-t!

We got pictures of ..... MCR.... Relient K..... Senses Fail.. and Hawthorne Heights... I think that's all.. and I got a MCR t-shirt along with a Warped tour '05 shirt. 

When we got home, we had Burger King. We were so hungry the only other time we ate was at 9 AM! We didn't want to spend money on food there - it's outragous! BUT there was free water... the only thing that sucked yesterday is that My Face Got FRIED! It's really red!

Other than that, it was awesome! I AM going back next year. It is soo0o0o0o0o0 worth it. but I will prolly try to save a little bit more money... so I can get more shirts... cds.. I will be prepared Tho - sunscreen... bag.... headache medicine.... and a hat! lol.

Background info first : Vincent's dad : truck driver and has no custody of Vince what so ever.

I found out from a friend, later on, that Vincent was forced to go with him and took only valuables.. I also heard they are heading towards Alaska.

 

Eeryone is upset. They called the cops. but I dont know anything else .. haven't got an update. I know he's ok.. but I'm still worried.
